        "supportText": "LÃNG PHÍ THỜI GIAN",
        "conceptColor": "#CC0000",
        "headType": "cracked",
        "posture": "slouched"
      },
      "startFrame": 832,
      "endFrame": 1052,
      "duration": 219
    },
    {
      "id": "S6",
      "template": "DarkBeat",
      "text": "I wasn't moving forward. I was just more confused. More exhausted.",
      "params": {
        "conceptWord": "BẾ TẮC",
        "supportText": "KIỆT SỨC & HỖN LOẠN",
        "conceptColor": "#CC0000",
        "headType": "cracked",
        "posture": "slouched"
      },
      "startFrame": 1052,
      "endFrame": 1251,
      "duration": 199
    },
    {
      "id": "S7",
      "template": "DarkBeat",
      "text": "And the worst part is, I started thinking: \"Is there something wrong with me?\" \"Do I lack discipline?\" \"Am I just not good enough to change?\"",
      "params": {
        "conceptWord": "HOÀI NGHI",
        "supportText": "TỰ VẤN BẢN THÂN",
        "conceptColor": "#CC0000",
        "headType": "cracked",
        "posture": "slouched"
      },
      "startFrame": 1251,
      "endFrame": 1529,
      "duration": 278
    },
    {
      "id": "S8",
      "template": "BigTextReveal",
      "text": "No. The problem isn't you.",
